\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6}{\ignorespaces The Co-responsibility Architecture (CRA) feedback loop. An AI-proposed mapping is reviewed by a human accountant. If the human override violates deterministic ontology rules (e.g., changing cash nature), the system forces the entry of an explanation, flags the transaction, and writes it to the immutable ledger for future auditor review.}}{20}{figure.6}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:cra_loop}{{6}{20}{The Co-responsibility Architecture (CRA) feedback loop. An AI-proposed mapping is reviewed by a human accountant. If the human override violates deterministic ontology rules (e.g., changing cash nature), the system forces the entry of an explanation, flags the transaction, and writes it to the immutable ledger for future auditor review}{figure.6}{}}
